Rulings.Base:
1. This card targets the 2 "Resonator" monsters.
2. Adding 1 Level 4 monster to your hand and returning the targeted monsters to your Deck occur simultaneously.
3. If only 1 of the target monsters is in your GY when this card resolves, you still return the remaining one to your Deck and add a monster to your hand.
4. If none of the target monsters remain in your GY when this card resolves, you still add a monster to your hand.
5. You cannot activate this card if you have no more Level 4 monsters in your Deck.
6. If you have no Level 4 monsters in your Deck when this card resolves, you don't return the target monsters to your Deck.
